# Paths excluded from the coverage gate (regex over coverage-profile lines).
# Keep this list small and well-justified.

# Entry point — flag parsing, signal handling, ListenAndServe wiring. The
# pure dispatch logic in run() is still tested (cmd/burnbox/main_test.go),
# but the serve/signal/shutdown plumbing has no behaviour worth a
# coverage-driven test.
github.com/kfet/burnbox/cmd/burnbox/main.go

# Frontend static-check helper — invoked via `make lint-frontend`, not
# exercised by go test.
github.com/kfet/burnbox/scripts/lintfrontend/main.go

# End-to-end test package — exercised by `make e2e`, not unit tests.
^github.com/kfet/burnbox/e2e/
